      • determine

        public Collection<ShipmentOutgoing> determine(DocumentHeader documentHeaderIn)
        Description copied from interface: OutgoingShipment

        Tries to create one ShipmentOutgoing for each recipient.

        The method can be called multiple times. Each next call determine next ShipmentOutgoing based on the state of previous ShipmentOutgoing.

        Specified by:
        determine in interface OutgoingShipment

      • determine

        protected ShipmentOutgoing determine(DocumentHeader documentHeaderIn,
                                     Participant participantIn)
        • 1. Find current bodies.
        • 2. Find endpoints where
          endpoint.documentFormat = body.documentFormat
          AND endpoint.participant = participant
        • 3. Create the ShipmentOutgoing.
